title: Newlyweds Leven Rambin and Jim Parrack Share Wedding Pictures
text:
Comments Leven Rambin and her new husband shares pictures and a video from their weekend nuptials in Texas. 
Leven Rambin and her new husband, Jim Parrack, are celebrating after tying the knot on Saturday, October 10 at Le San Michele in Buda, Texas. " The Hunger Games " actress and the " True Blood " actor share on Instagram their wedding pictures and the first look at their wedding bands. "Thank you for marrying me @parrack120!!!! I love you, husband!" the bride captioned one of their wedding photos. She also uploaded a video of them singing and dancing to Journey 's "Don't Stop Believin' " at the party, "Our wedding turned into a mosh pit of love and joy Doesn't get better anywhere on EARTH!"
